<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Registration Update</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f7fa;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4caf50, #2e7d32);
        padding: 28px 32px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 32px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .content p {
        margin: 16px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      .reason-box {
        margin: 24px 0;
        padding: 18px;
        background: #fff6e9;
        border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #795548;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f0f4f8;
        padding: 20px 32px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #607d8b;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .cta {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        background: #4caf50;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Registration Requires Updates</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>
          Thank you for registering with the Waste Scheduling and Billing System. After reviewing
          your submission, we need a few updates before we can activate your account.
        </p>
        {{#if reason}}
        <div class="reason-box">
          <strong>What needs attention:</strong>
          <p>{{reason}}</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        <p>
          Please reply to this email or reach out to us at {{supportEmail}} once the requested
          updates are ready. Our team will re-evaluate your registration promptly.
        </p>
        <p>
          We appreciate your patience and look forward to welcoming you to the platform soon.
        </p>
        <a class="cta" href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">Contact Support</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        Waste Scheduling and Billing System<br />
        Keeping communities clean and connected.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
